Package com.tsuboin.exceptions

  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    DuplicateSiteException
    DuplicateSiteExceptions are thrown when the supplied site is already stored in the vault for that user.
    DuplicateUserException
    DuplicateUserExceptions are thrown when the username is already in the vault.
    InvalidPasswordException
    InvalidPasswordExceptions are thrown when the supplied password is invalid.
    InvalidSiteException
    InvalidSiteExceptions are thrown when the site name supplied is invalid.
    InvalidUsernameException
    InvalidUsernameExceptions are thrown by classes implemented over the Vault interface when a username that doesn't not meet the criteria is entered.
    PasswordMismatchException
    InvalidPasswordExceptions are thrown when the password supplied does not match the user's vault password.
    SiteNotFoundException
    SiteNotFoundExceptions are thrown when the user has no password associated with this site.
    UserLockedOutException
    UserLockedOutExceptions are thrown when the user has entered too many incorrect login attempts.
    UserNotFoundException
    UserNotFoundExceptions are thrown when there is no such user in the vault.
